flowchart TD
  U[ADMIN / DOCTOR / PATIENT] --> C[Medical Record Servlet]
  C --> S[MedicalRecordService]
  S --> O{Role and ownership?}
  O -- No --> D[403-safe response + access audit]
  O -- Yes --> A[AppointmentDao]
  A --> E{CONFIRMED or COMPLETED?}
  E -- No --> B[Creation blocked + audit]
  E -- Yes --> Q{Record already exists?}
  Q -- Yes --> DUP[Duplicate response]
  Q -- No --> M[MedicalRecordDao transaction]
  M --> DB[(Oracle XE)]
  S --> DR[DoctorDao]
  S --> PR[PatientDao]
  PR --> RO[Patient read-only view]
